reviewText:
THE CLASSIC T.D JAKES ARE ABSOLUTELY THE BEST,THE CURRENT ONES TOO, BUT THE CLASSICS CONTAIN POWERFUL MESSAGES FROM THE SERMON-CHOSEN,COURAGE IN A CRISIS,GET IN THE BIRTH POSITION,THE PLIGHT OF THE SCARLET HOUSEWIFE,BAD BOYS AND THE GOD WHO LOVES THEM AND TELL THE DEVIL I CHANGED MY MIND.
IF YOU ARE DEBATING PURCHASING THIS SERIES PLEASE DO YOU WILL NOT REGRET IT.

  ENJOY!
